dents   UIC Business students should continue to monitor their UIC email and follow UIC campus and guidance on COVID-19 Policies. The campus website in the link above is the first and main place you should be consulting for information regarding this dynamic situation.  As stated in the March 12 note from campus, classes are converting to online formats as quickly as possible, but no later than March 30, with the exception of some science labs and clinical courses. Please stay in communication with your instructors and departments for course specific information.         UIC Information: Coronavirus 2020         Pride Points        Top 20 %   Best Undergraduate Business Programs
